---
import LayoutFunnel from '@/layouts/LayoutFunnel.astro';
---

<LayoutFunnel title="Clinic Revenue Architecture | Marketing by Besic">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl text-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-brand/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="heading-xl mb-6">
        Your Clinic Is Leaking EUR 200K+ Per Year. We Know Exactly Where.
      </h1>
      <p class="body-lg mb-12">
        Not a guess. Not a theory. A forensic revenue diagnostic that maps every leak in your patient acquisition system -- from first click to paid treatment.
      </p>

      <!-- Hero Image -->
      <img src="/offer-clinics-hero.webp" alt="Clinic Revenue Architecture" class="w-full rounded-lg mb-12 object-cover max-h-[500px]" width="1200" height="500" loading="eager" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">Three Revenue Leaks Draining Your Clinic Right Now</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-brand">Leak 1: Generic Follow-Up Sequences</h3>
          <p class="body-md">
            60% of your leads never book because your follow-up sequence treats a Botox inquiry the same as a rhinoplasty consultation. Generic nurture emails don't convert high-consideration medical decisions. Your CRM is full of leads. Your calendar is not.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-brand">Leak 2: Ads Optimized for Clicks, Not Patients</h3>
          <p class="body-md">
            Your agency reports on impressions and click-through rates. But you can't eat clicks. You need patients who show up, pay, and return for follow-up treatments. Your ads optimize for the wrong metric, and you're subsidizing the cost.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-brand">Leak 3: No Closed-Loop Tracking</h3>
          <p class="body-md">
            You can't tell which campaigns produce paying patients. Your Google Ads account says "247 conversions." Your accountant says revenue is flat. The gap between reported conversions and actual revenue is where your marketing budget dies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem Image -->
      <img src="/offer-clinics-problem.webp" alt="Clinic revenue leak diagnosis" class="w-full rounded-lg my-12 object-cover max-h-[300px]" width="1200" height="300" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">The Patient Revenue Architecture</h2>

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 1: Patient Revenue Diagnostic</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              We map every leak in your booking flow -- from ad impression to booked treatment to follow-up visit. No ad spend. No commitment. We find EUR 25K+ in recoverable revenue or you pay nothing. You'll know exactly where the money is going before we touch a single campaign.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 2: NLP-Optimized Patient Acquisition</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              Treatment-specific follow-up sequences that match the decision psychology of each procedure. Ads rebuilt to optimize for patients who actually show up and pay -- not clicks, not form fills, not "conversions" that never convert to revenue.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 3: Closed-Loop Revenue Tracking</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              Every ad euro traced to every patient euro. No vanity dashboards. No "estimated" ROI. Your EMR data connected to your ad accounts so you see which campaigns produce paying patients, which produce time-wasters, and which produce nothing at all.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Solution Image -->
      <img src="/offer-clinics-solution.webp" alt="Patient Revenue Architecture system" class="w-full rounded-lg my-12 object-cover max-h-[300px]" width="1200" height="300" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Execution Gap Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#111111] relative z-10">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">Most Agencies Deliver Reports. We Deliver Revenue.</h2>
      <p class="body-md mb-6 text-center">
        The gap between knowing your leaks and fixing them is where clinics die slowly. Your last agency gave you a 47-page deck. Your revenue didn't move. Our framework closes the execution gap by building the infrastructure, connecting the tracking, and optimizing every touchpoint in your patient journey.
      </p>
      <p class="body-md mb-6 text-center font-semibold text-brand">
        We positioned a medical device company across 21 countries using this framework. Your clinic is next.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 pb-48">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-6">Apply for a Revenue Diagnosis</h2>
      <p class="body-lg mb-12">
        We take on 3 clinic clients per quarter. If your clinic generates EUR 500K+ annually and you suspect your patient acquisition system is underperforming, apply below.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center w-full">
        <a
          href="/en/apply"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 bg-[#8224e3] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#6a1ca6] hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(130,36,227,0.4)]"
        >
          Apply for Revenue Diagnosis
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutFunnel>
